STATE
v.
Quentin T. WILLIAMSON. No. 139P06-2. Supreme Court of North Carolina. October 11, 2007. Thomas J. Ziko, Special Deputy Attorney General, William D. Kenerly, District Attorney, for State of NC.

The following order has been entered on the motion filed on the 13th day of September 2007 by Defendant for "Petition for Discretionary Review":

"Motion Dismissed by order of the Court in conference this the 11th day of October 2007."
